Package: libapriltag-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libapriltag3 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Visual fiducial system for robotics - development files
 AprilTag is a visual fiducial system, useful for a wide variety of
 tasks including augmented reality, robotics, and camera calibration.
 .
 This package contains header and development runtime.

