Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Visual fiducial system for robotics - runtime
 AprilTag is a visual fiducial system, useful for a wide variety of
 tasks including augmented reality, robotics, and camera calibration.
 .
 This package contains the C optimized runtime
